      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", etc.: first He asks a question as to the legality of Sabbatic healing in a tone which amounts to an affirmative assertion, allowed to pass uncontradicted (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ἡσύχασαν",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "); then He proceeds to answer His own question by healing the man (",
        "children": []
